This paper deals with the issue of imbalanced dataset in multi-label text categorization, which is a common problem in information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also employs machine learning algorithms such as Bagging and Adaptive Boosting, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper evaluates the performance of the algorithms using various evaluation metrics, which is related to data science (cs.DS).
